652
00:48:56,879 --> 00:48:59,250
Mungkin sesuatu terjadi kepada Jin U.

653
00:49:00,909 --> 00:49:02,279
Kita akan tahu saat tiba di sana.

654
00:49:38,720 --> 00:49:39,919
Ibu.

655
00:49:43,360 --> 00:49:46,230
Aku hanya sebentar meninggalkannya. Aku di sini selama ini.

656
00:49:51,230 --> 00:49:52,370
Hwa Young.

657
00:49:53,129 --> 00:49:54,429
Kamu kenapa?

658
00:49:55,000 --> 00:49:56,139
Kalian berdua

659
00:49:56,840 --> 00:49:58,269
